msgctxt "bayesianStateSpace|"
msgid ""
"This component allows you to model the effect of covariates or fixed factors "
"on the dependent variable. The lag of coefficients can be specified to "
"account for delayed effects. Only available when covariates or fixed factors "
"are present in the model."
msgstr ""
"此成分可用於建模共變數或固定因子對依變數的影響。可指定係數的落後期，以納入延"
"遲效果。僅在模型中包含共變數或固定因子時可用。"
